message: Unauthorized users are posting inaccurate information about Claudia Mason. STOP.

We are Claudia Mason’s representatives. We were just alerted that some entity, perhaps named: Swadge2 is falsely posting information about Ms. Mason without any authority to do so. They must immediately stop posting unauthorized information about Ms. Mason or we will report them.

We are Ms Mason’s representatives. We’re correcting incorrect information that we recently discovered was uploaded to her page. We advise all entities who upload inaccurate information about public figures such as Ms Mason, to immediately stop. Further action will be taken against such people if necessary.
